A video has surfaced on the social media of a taxi assistant assaulting two school girls in uniform.The man shows no mercy as he punch, kick and slaps one of the girls before another girl intervenes to try and help her colleague but she is dealt with mercilessly. She gets tripped to the floor and assaulted heavily.The assault only stops when another man pushes the assistant back into the taxi and closes the door.It is not known where exactly in South Africa this happened.It&#8217;s just another of many incidents that women are abused by the taxi men. In another video that also went viral on the internet, a woman was ruthlessly assaulted by a taxi driver.The man was later fired from his job by his boss who condemned his brutal attack on a defenceless woman.Watch video below: https://youtu.be/dQtNyCcJgl4